| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3879 — Recovery Inhibition (blacklock)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e3c0812e-8c4f-5f4b-8c80-716ed272dc21"
